Package: LRnetST
Type: Package
Title: LRnetST
Version: 2.1
Date: 2026-05-04
Author: Jie Peng
Maintainer: Jie Peng <jiepeng@ucdavis.edu>
Description: Package for learning directed acyclic graphs from spatial
    transcriptomics data (zero-inflated mixed continuous/binary nodes), with
    improved score caching, acyclicity cache correctness fixes, and future-based
    parallel bootstrap aggregation.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.4)
Suggests: future, testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen, RcppNumerical
